GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_drafting_24.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Extra time.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_drafting_25.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You're using extra time.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_drafting_26.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Reserve time.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_drafting_27.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You're using reserve time.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Etc_01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|The game already started, by the way. I wasn't sure if you were waiting for a whistle. There isn't one.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_001.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Thanks to you.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_002.wav |GLaDOS|EN|That's bad, by the way.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_004.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You're allowed to defend those, you know.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_005.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Because of poor decisions. Yours, most likely.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_006.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Just abandon, no one will even notice.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_007.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Because someone... I'm talking about you here... doesn't know what they're doing.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_008.wav |GLaDOS|EN|What counts is that you tried, so maybe do that next time.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_009.wav |GLaDOS|EN|There are no handicaps on this match, by the way. You can stop them from doing that.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_010.wav |GLaDOS|EN|If you were saving your real strategy for a crisis, now would be the time.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_011.wav |GLaDOS|EN|That outfit you're wearing looks stupid. That's not me talking, it's right here in your file.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_012.wav |GLaDOS|EN|When other people play that hero, it looks fine. But right here, a scientist has noted that when you play it looks stupid.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_013.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Grief counseling will be available at the conclusion of the match.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_014.wav |GLaDOS|EN|But on the bright side, I just won... money... gambling money... by betting against you.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_015.wav |GLaDOS|EN|But we're all winners here. Especially those players over there, in the enemy camp. You know, the ones celebrating.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_016.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Interesting strategy. Let them obliterate all your defenses, then swoop in for the kill.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_017.wav |GLaDOS|EN|That doesn't mean you have to like it, it just means you'll probably keep doing it because of your aptitude at failure.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_018.wav |GLaDOS|EN|But don't worry, losing builds character. In fact, it's making you a better person right now. A great, big, well rounded loser, with lots of personality.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_019.wav |GLaDOS|EN|But looking at it another way, I think you've won a real moral victory here. Which doesn't mean we should forget about the first way, the more accurate and humiliating way.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_020.wav |GLaDOS|EN|But it's not a big loss, really. It's one in a series of very small losses over a forty-five minute time-span that, when added up, will look like one big, spectacular failure.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_021.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Well, nobody will hold it against you. Let's be honest, I doubt anyone will even find it surprising.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_022.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Now you're really in for it.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_023.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I can't even begin to describe how badly you've screwed this up. Oh wait, I just did.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_024.wav |GLaDOS|EN|If I was a betting artificial intelligence, I'd put money on them killing you now.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_025.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Thats bad, by the way.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_026.wav |GLaDOS|EN|That doesn't mean you have to like it.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_027.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Don't get cocky.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_028.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Don't let it go to your fat, jowly head.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_029.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Don't let it go to your giant, misshapen, fantasy head.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_030.wav |GLaDOS|EN|So, at least your teammates know what they're doing.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_031.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You're winning the epic battle for this small field, with a creek running through it.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_Dota_2_Followup_032.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Here, let me engrave a trophy for you. "Nobody cares.
