GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_hub_return05a.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Welcome back to the hub, did you fail at selecting the correct course?
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_hub_return06a.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Was that course too difficult?
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_hubreturn01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Look who's back, were you scared to continue those tests?
