GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_hubreturn07.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I guess quitting that course together is a sign of teamwork.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_hubreturn08.wav |GLaDOS|EN|The way you two just gave up on that test together shows you are really working as a team.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_hubreturn09.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Are you scared to save those humans?
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_hubreturn10.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Are you scared to save those humans?
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_hubreturn11.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Blue, I wouldn't have trusted Orange in that course either.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_humanresources01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Did you know we originally used these cameras to capture moments of intense pain and agony in test subjects?
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_humanresources03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|If the subject survived the test, we let them purchase the pictures for $5. If the subject died, we gave the photo to their next of kin free of charge.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_humanresources04.wav |GLaDOS|EN|The photos weren't as popular as we had hoped, so we repurposed the cameras.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfuge_misc05.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Credit where credit's due: you're both doing a great job of disappointing me.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfuge_misc06.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I just hate Blue a little more.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfuge_misc07.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I've been doing some reading. Did you know that the word orange is derived from the same Latin root as the word traitor?
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfuge_misc11.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Watching you try to sabotage one other, I'm amazed you're still on friendly terms.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfuge_misc14.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Blue, please disregard the following statement: Orange, you have been a shining light in an otherwise ungodly morass of incompetence.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfuge_misc16.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I would prefer to speak to one of you in private but since that is not an option here, I will speak in code that only one of you will understand. Blue: Orange is plotting to destroy you.
