GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfuge02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Orange, it's not nice to make fun of Blue like that.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfuge03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Yes Orange, we are alone. Blue can't hear you.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfuge04.wav |GLaDOS|EN|That's horrible.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfuge05.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I can only imagine.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfuge06.wav |GLaDOS|EN|What a horrible little machine.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfuge07.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Correct Blue, Orange can't hear you.
