GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfuge35.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Without the consequence of death, is this even science?
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfuge36.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I have noticed you two have become extremely close. I'm not sure I like that.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfuge39.wav |GLaDOS|EN|While teamwork is needed to complete these tests, I am not sure I trust the two of you together.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfuge44.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Blue, do you feel betrayed by orange for telling me those horrible things about you?
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfuge45.wav |GLaDOS|EN|If Orange had said those things about me, Orange would never make it to the next reassembly station.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfuge46.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Orange, do you feel betrayed by Blue for telling me those horrible things about you?
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfuge47.wav |GLaDOS|EN|If Blue had said those things about me, Blue would never make it to the next reassembly station.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfugedeath_blue01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You were right, Orange. Blue was dumb enough to fall for your trap.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfugedeath_blue02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Orange, that transpired just as you said it would.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfugedeath_blue03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I agree, Orange. That was entertaining.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfugedeath_blue04.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Yes Orange, Blue did act like a fool just now.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfugedeath_orange02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Blue, that transpired just as you said it would.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfugedeath_orange03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I agree, Blue. That was entertaining.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfugedeath_orange06.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Yes, I know you did that, Blue. Don't look so proud.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_subterfugedeath_orange08.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Blue, being the last one standing is not the goal.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_taunts01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Come on. You were raised better than that.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_taunts02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Even humans, as stupid as they are, would say you look stupid when you do that.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_taunts03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You're doing a great job of disappointing me.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_taunts04.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Your eagerness to test pleases me. Your inane gesturing does not.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_taunts05.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Is it the lack of mirrors in test chambers that encourages you to do this?
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_mp_taunts06.wav |GLaDOS|EN|DANCING is NOT SCIENCE!
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_multiple_spheres01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Begin juggling test in three. Two. One.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_potatos_fgb_confrontation07.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You didn't do anything.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_potatos_fgb_confrontation08.wav |GLaDOS|EN|She did all the work.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_prehub04.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Commence standing by in three. Two. One.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_prehub14.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You performed this test better than anyone on record. This is a pre-recorded message.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_prehub15.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Due to events beyond our control, some testing environments may contain flood damage or ongoing tribal warfare resulting from the collapse of civilization.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_prehub16.wav |GLaDOS|EN|If groups of hunter-gatherers appear to have made this - or any - test chamber their home, DO NOT AGITATE THEM. Test through them.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_prehub24.wav |GLaDOS|EN|In the event that the Enrichment Center is currently being bombarded with fireballs, meteorites, or other objects from space, please avoid unsheltered testing areas wherever a lack of shelter from space-debris DOES NOT appear to be a deliberate part of the test.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_prehub26.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You have just passed through an Aperture Science Material Emancipation Grill, which erases most Aperture Science equipment that touches it.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_prehub27.wav |GLaDOS|EN|If you feel liquid running down your neck, relax, lie on your back, and apply immediate pressure to your temples.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_prehub28.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You are simply experiencing a rare reaction, in which the Material Emancipation Grill may have erased the ear tubes inside your head.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_prehub29.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Because this message is prerecorded, the Enrichment Center has no way of knowing if whatever government remains offers any sort of Cattle Tuberculosis Testing Credit for taxes.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_prehub30.wav |GLaDOS|EN|In the event that it does, this next test involves exposure to cattle tuberculosis. Good luck!
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_prehub32.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Very impressive! Because this message is prerecorded, any comments we may make about your success are speculation on our part. Please disregard any undeserved compliments.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_prehub34.wav |GLaDOS|EN|This next test applies the principles of momentum to movement through portals. If the laws of physics no longer apply in the future, God help you.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_prehub35.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Congratulations! This pre-recorded congratulations assumes you have mastered the principles of portal momentum.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_prehub36.wav |GLaDOS|EN|If you have, in fact, not, you are encouraged to take a moment to reflect on your failure before proceeding into the next chamber.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_prehub47.wav |GLaDOS|EN|In order to ensure that sufficient power remains for core testing protocols, all safety devices have been disabled.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_prehub48.wav |GLaDOS|EN|The Enrichment Center respects your right to have questions or concerns about this policy.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_prehub55.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Excellent. The Enrichment Center reminds you that bold, persistent experimentation is the hallmark of good science.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_prehub56.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Well done. In the event that oxygen is no longer available in the Enrichment Center, an auxiliary air supply will be provided to you by an Aperture Science Test Associate, if one exists.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a1_wakeup_incinerator01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I will say, though, that since you went to all the trouble of waking me up, you must really, really love to test.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a1_wakeup_incinerator02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I love it, too. So let's get you a dual portal device and go do some science.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_bridge_intro01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|These bridges are made from natural light that I pump in from the surface. If you rubbed your cheek on one, it would be like standing outside with the sun shining on your face. It would also set your hair on fire, so don't actually do it.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_bridge_intro03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Excellent! You're a predator and these tests are your prey. Speaking of which, I was researching sharks for an upcoming test. Do you know who else murders people who are only trying to help them?
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_bridge_intro04.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Did you guess 'sharks'? Because that's wrong. The correct answer is 'nobody.' Nobody but you is that pointlessly cruel.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_bridge_the_gap01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Good news. I figured out what to do with all the money I save recycling your one roomful of air. When you die, I'm going to laminate your skeleton and pose you in the lobby. That way future generations can learn from you how not to have your unfortunate bone structure.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_bridge_the_gap02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Perfect, the door's malfunctioning. I guess somebody is going to have to repair it. No, it's okay, I'll do that too. I'll be right back. Don't touch anything.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_bts1_intro01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I've got a surprise for you after this next test. Not a fake, tragic surprise like last time. A real surprise, with tragic consequences. And real confetti this time. The good stuff. Our last bag. Part of me's going to miss it, I guess-but at the end of the day it was just taking up space.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_catapult01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Here's an interesting fact: you're not breathing real air. It's too expensive to pump this far down. We just take carbon dioxide out of a room, freshen it up a little, and pump it back in. So you'll be breathing the same room full of air for the rest of your life. I thought that was interesting.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_column_blocker01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Oh come on... If it makes you feel any better, they abandoned you at birth, so I very seriously doubt they'd even want to see you.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_column_blocker03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I feel awful about that surprise. Tell you what, let's give your parents a call right now. [phone ringing] The birth parents you are trying to reach do not love you. Please hang up. [Dial tone]
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_column_blocker04.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Oh, that's sad. But impressive. Maybe they worked at the phone company.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_column_blocker05.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Well, you know the old formula: Comedy equals tragedy plus time. And you have been asleep for a while. So I guess it's actually pretty funny when you do the math.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_core01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Don't you DARE plug him in.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_core02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Do NOT plug that little idiot into MY mainframe.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_core03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Don't plug him in.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_core04.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Don't plug him in.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_dilemma01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I thought about our dilemma, and I came up with a solution that I honestly think works out best for one of both of us.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_dual_lasers_intro01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Don't let that 'horrible person' thing discourage you. It's just a data point. If it makes you feel any better, science has now validated your birth mother's decision to abandon you on a doorstep.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_fizzler_intro01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|This next test involves emancipation grills. Remember? I told you about them in the last test area, that did not have one.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_fizzler_intro04.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Ohhh, no. The turbines again. I have to go. Wait. This next test DOES require some explanation. Let me give you the fast version.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_fizzler_intro06.wav |GLaDOS|EN|There. If you have any questions, just remember what I said in slow motion. Test on your own recognizance, I'll be right back.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_future_starter01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|If you think trapping yourself is going to make me stop testing, you're sorely mistaken. Here's another cube.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_intro1_found01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Good. You have a dual portal device. There should be a way back to the testing area up ahead.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_intro1_found05.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You know, if you'd done that to somebody else, they might devote their existences to exacting revenge.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_intro1_found06.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Luckily I'm a bigger person than that. I'm happy to put this all behind us and get back to work. After all, we've got a lot to do, and only sixty more years to do it. More or less. I don't have the actuarial tables in front of me.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_intro1_found07.wav |GLaDOS|EN|But the important thing is you're back. With me. And now I'm onto all your little tricks. So there's nothing to stop us from testing for the rest of your life.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_intro1_found08.wav |GLaDOS|EN|After that...who knows? I might take up a hobby. Reanimating the dead, maybe.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_laser_over_goo_intro01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You're navigating these test chambers faster than I can build them. So feel free to slow down and... do whatever it is you do when you're not destroying this facility.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_laser_stairs_intro02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|This next test involves discouragement redirection cubes. I'd just finished building them before you had your, well, episode. So now we'll both get to see how they work.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_laser_stairs_intro03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|There should be one in the corner.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_pit_flings_future_starter01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Uh oh. You're stranded. Let's see if the cube will try to help you escape. Actually, so that we're not here all day, I'll just cut to the chase: It won't. Any feelings you think it has for you are simply byproducts of your sad, empty life.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_pit_flings_future_starter02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Anyway, here's a new cube for you to project your deranged loneliness onto.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_pit_flings01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Hmm. This emancipation grill is broken.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_pit_flings02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Don't take anything with you.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_pit_flings03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Every test chamber is equipped with an emancipation grill at its exit, so that test subjects can't smuggle test objects out of the test area. This one is broken.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_pit_flings06.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I think that one was about to say 'I love you.' They ARE sentient, of course. We just have a LOT of them.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_ricochet01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Enjoy this next test. I'm going to go to the surface. It's a beautiful day out. Yesterday I saw a deer. If you solve this next test, maybe I'll let you ride an elevator all the way up to the break room, and I'll tell you about the time I saw a deer again.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_trust_fling01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Oh, sorry. I'm still cleaning out the test chambers.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_trust_fling02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|So sometimes there's still trash in them. Standing around. Smelling, and being useless.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_trust_fling03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Try to avoid the garbage hurtling towards you.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_trust_fling04.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You don't have to test with the garbage. It's garbage.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_trust_fling06.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Remember before when I was talking about smelly garbage standing around being useless? That was a metaphor. I was actually talking about you. And I'm sorry. You didn't react at the time, so I was worried it sailed right over your head. Which would have made this apology seem insane. That's why I had to call you garbage a second time just now.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_turret_blocker_future_starter01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Oops. You trapped yourself. I guess that's it then. Thanks for testing. You may as well lie down and get acclimated to the being dead position.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_turret_blocker_future_starter02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I'm kidding. Not about you trapping yourself, though. That really happened. Here, I'll lower the glass. Go on... Finish the test.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_turret_intro01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|That jumpsuit you're wearing looks stupid. That's not me talking, it's right here in your file. On other people it looks fine, but right here a scientist has noted that on you it looks 'stupid.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_a2_turret_intro03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Well, what does a neck-bearded old engineer know about fashion? He probably - Oh, wait. It's a she. Still, what does she know? Oh wait, it says she has a medical degree. In fashion! From France!
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_box_over_goo01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Oh. You survived. That's interesting. I guess I should have factored in your weight.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_box_over_goo04.wav |GLaDOS|EN|One of these times you'll be so fat that you'll jump, and you'll just drop like a stone. Into acid, probably. Like a potato into a deep fat fryer.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_bridge_intro_completion02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Say. Remember when we cleared the air back there? Is there... anything you want to say to me? Anything?
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_bridge_intro_completion03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Hold on, I'll stop the elevator. Anything? Take your time...
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_bridge_intro_completion04.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Well... I'll be here during the whole next test.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_catapult_fling_sphere_peek_completion01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Look at you. Sailing through the air majestically. Like an eagle. Piloting a blimp.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_catapult_fling_sphere_peek_failureone01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Well, I'm back. The Aerial Faith Plate in here is sending a distress signal.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_catapult_fling_sphere_peek_failureone02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You broke it, didn't you.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_catapult_fling_sphere_peek_failureone03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|There. Try it now.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_catapult_fling_sphere_peek_failurethree01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You seem to have defeated its load-bearing capacity. Well done. I'll just lower the ceiling.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_catapult_fling_sphere_peek_failuretwo01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Hmm. This Plate must not be calibrated to someone of your... generous... ness. I'll add a few zeros to the maximum weight.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_catapult_fling_sphere_peek_failuretwo03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Try it now.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_catapult_intro_completion01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Let's see what the next test is. Oh. Advanced Aerial Faith Plates.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_column_blocker_entry01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|It's healthy for you to have other friends. To look for qualities in other people that I obviously lack.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_hole_in_the_sky_completion01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Well done. You know, when I woke up and saw the state of the labs, I started to wonder if there was any point to going on. I came THAT close to just giving up and letting you go.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_hole_in_the_sky_completion02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|But now, looking around, seeing Aperture restored to its former glory? You don't have to worry about leaving EVER again. I mean that.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_hole_in_the_sky_entry01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Federal regulations require me to warn you that this next test chamber... is looking pretty good.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_hole_in_the_sky_entry02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|That's right. Drink it in. You could eat off those wall panels.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_incinerator_01_01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Here we are. The Incinerator Room. Be careful not to trip over any parts of me that didn't get completely burned when you threw them down here.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_incinerator_01_03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|There it is.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_incinerator_01_04.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Hold on...
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_incinerator_01_05.wav |GLaDOS|EN|There.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_incinerator_01_08.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Once testing starts, I'm required by protocol to keep interaction with you to a minimum. Luckily, we haven't started testing yet. This will be our only chance to talk.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_incinerator_01_09.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Do you know the biggest lesson I learned from what you did? I discovered I have a sort of black-box quick-save feature. In the event of a catastrophic failure, the last two minutes of my life are preserved for analysis.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_incinerator_01_10.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I was able - well, forced really - to relive you killing me. Again and again. Forever.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_incinerator_01_11.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Fifty thousand years is a lot of time to think. About me. About you. We were doing so well together.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_incinerator_01_12.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Here, let me get that for you.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_incinerator_01_13.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I'll just move that out of the way for you. This place really is a wreck.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_incinerator_01_15.wav |GLaDOS|EN|We're a lot alike, you and I. You tested me. I tested you. You killed me. I--oh, no, wait. I guess I HAVEN'T killed you yet. Well. Food for thought.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_incinerator_01_18.wav |GLaDOS|EN|The dual portal device should be around here somewhere. Once you find it, we can start testing. Just like old times.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_laser_over_goo_completion01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I'll give you credit: I guess you ARE listening to me. But for the record: You don't have to go THAT slowly.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_laser_powered_lift_completion01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I have the results of the last chamber: You are a horrible person. That's what it says: A horrible person. We weren't even testing for that.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_laser_powered_lift_completion02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Well done. Here come the test results: You are a horrible person. I'm serious, that's what it says: A horrible person. We weren't even testing for that.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_laser_powered_lift_entry01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|This next test may result in your death. If you want to know what that's like, think back to that time you killed me, and substitute yourself for me.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_laser_redirect_intro_completion01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Congratulations. Not on the test.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_laser_redirect_intro_completion03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Most people emerge from suspension terribly undernourished. I want to congratulate you on beating the odds and somehow managing to pack on a few pounds.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_laserfield_intro01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Per our last conversation: You're also ugly. I'm looking at your file right now, and it mentions that more than once.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_paint_jump_redirect_bomb_completion01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I thought we could test like we used to. But I'm discovering things about you that I never saw before. We can't ever go back to the way it was.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_paint_jump_redirect_bomb_entry01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You can't keep going like this forever, you know. I'm GOING to find out what you're doing. Out there. Where I can't see you. I'll know. All I need is proof.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_paint_jump_trampoline_completion01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Just so you know, I have to go give a deposition. For an upcoming trial. In case that interests you.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_paint_jump_trampoline_entry01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|While I was out investigating, I found a fascinating new test element. It's never been used for human testing because, apparently, contact with it causes heart failure. The literature doesn't mention anything about lump-of-coal failure, though, so you should be fine.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_paint_jump_wall_jumps02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I'm sorry, I don't know why that went off. Anyway, just an interesting science fact.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_sabotage_glados_confused04.wav |GLaDOS|EN|...What are you doing?...
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_sabotage_glados_dropped01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|AHH!
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_shoot_through_wall_completion01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Did my hint help? It did, didn't it? You know, if any of our supervisors had been immune to neurotoxin, they'd be FURIOUS with us right now.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_shoot_through_wall_entry01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You know, I'm not supposed to do this, but... you can shoot SOMETHING... through the blue bridges.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_sphere_2nd_encounter_completion01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You really are doing great... Chell.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_sphere_2nd_encounter_entry01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I shouldn't spoil this, but... remember how I'm going to live forever, but you're going to be dead in sixty years? Well, I've been working on a present for you. Well, I guess it's more of a medical procedure. Well, technically it's more of a medical experiment. You know how excruciating it is when someone removes all of your bone marrow? Well, what if after I did that, I put something back IN that added four years to your life?
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_sphere_2nd_encounter_entrytwo01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I went and spoke with the door mainframe. Let's just say he won't be... well, living anymore. Anyway, back to testing.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_sphere_2nd_encounter_malfunction01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Ohhhh. Another door malfunction. I'm going to take care of this once and for all. Stay here, I'll be back in a while.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_sphere_2nd_encounter_malfunction02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Miss you!
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_trust_fling_entry01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Well. Have fun soaring through the air without a care in the world.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_trust_fling_entry02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|*I* have to go to the wing that was made entirely of glass and pick up fifteen acres of broken glass. By myself.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_trust_fling_sphereinterrupt01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Perfect, the door's malfunctioning. I guess somebody's going to have to repair that too. No, don't get up. I'll be right back. Don't touch anything.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_trust_fling_sphereinterrupt03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Nevermind. I have to go... check something. Test on your own recognizance. I'll be back.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_turret_intro_entry01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I wouldn't have warned you about this before, back when we hated each other. But those turrets are firing real bullets. So look out. I'd hate for something tragic to happen to you before I extract all your bone marrow.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_turret_islands01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I'm going to be honest with you now. Not fake honest like before, but real honest, like you're incapable of. I know you're up to something.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_turret_islands02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|And as soon as I can PROVE it, the laws of robotics allow me to terminate you for being a liar.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_sp_unassisted_angle_fling_entry01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|This next test... [boom!] ..is... [BOOM!] dangerous. I'll be right back.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_big_wave01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Keep it up and your arm will get stuck like that.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_big_wave02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Hellllooo, imbecile.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_big_wave05.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Yes, I see you.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_big_wave06.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I'm seriously not paying atten-- STOP THAT RIGHT NOW!
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_big_wave07.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Yes, I see you waving.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_cannonball01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Good job jumping. You must be very proud.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_cannonball02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I hardly think you're even trying with these gestures anymore.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_cannonball03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Did something happen? [yawn] I wasn't watching.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_highfive01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|That is not part of the test.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_highfive03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Slapping hands. That accomplishes something.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_highfive04.wav |GLaDOS|EN|If you're going to hit each other, at least aim for the head.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_laugh01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You know what makes me laugh? The thought of you stopping that.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_laugh02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You know what makes me laugh? The thought of you cutting that out.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_laugh03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Ha ha ha ha ha, good one.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_laugh05.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Yes. Let's all laugh. Ha. Ha. Ha.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_laugh06.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Ha ha ha ha ha. Did I tell you the one about the turned-off reassembly machine?
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_robot_arm_ripple01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Are you broken? It looks like you're malfunctioning.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_robot_arm_ripple02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Really, not even humans do that anymore.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_robot_arm_ripple03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You're no longer bothering me. You're only hurting my impression of you.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_robot_arm_ripple04.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Look at you. Dancing.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_robot_arm_ripple05.wav |GLaDOS|EN|If you were wondering how could you annoy me without failing a test. Now you know.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_robot_arm_ripple06.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Oh great, dancing again.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_rockpaperscissors01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I defy you to tell me there's a purpose to what you're doing.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_small_wave_portalgun01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Are you trying to get my attention? I am very busy, you know.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_small_wave_portalgun02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Not paying attennnntion...
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_small_wave_portalgun03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Are you expecting applause?
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_small_wave01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Yes, I see you, and no, I don't care.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_small_wave02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Yes? Something you need?
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_small_wave03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You do know I can't wave back right?
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_small_wave04.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Stop with the waves.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_somersault01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I give you a score of 3.4 for style and 10 for being annoying.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_somersault02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|A somersault is just falling over in style. Congratulations on being clumsy.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_somersault03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|If I stop watching, I'm sure you'll get bored of this.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_splits01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|All right. I'm officially no longer paying attention to you.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_splits02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|All right. I'm officially no longer paying attention to you.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_splits03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You're the type of show-off who only shows off really stupid things.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_teamhug01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|It appears you're developing human traits. The worst human traits.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_teamhug02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Be careful. Hugging can lead to... well, me disassembling you forever.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_teamhug03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Stop touching each other!
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_teamtease01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Are you trying to impress me? What would impress me more is if you never did that again.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_teamtease02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I'll interpret that gesture to mean that you want me to become even more vindictive toward you.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_teamtease03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Orange, I certainly expected more from you.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_teamtease04.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Blue, don't sink to Orange's level.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_trickfire_handstand01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Now you're thinking with stupidity.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_trickfire_handstand02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Now you're just not thinking.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_trickfire_handstand03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Congratulations. You're upside down now.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_trickfire_handstand04.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You're going to hurt yourself doing that and then I will be ECSTATIC.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_taunt_trickfire_handstand05.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I'm starting to think giving you arms was a big mistake.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_testchambermisc02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Did you know I discovered a way to eradicate poverty? But then you KILLED me. So that's gone.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_testchambermisc12.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Waddle over to the elevator and we'll continue the testing.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_testchambermisc15.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Anything? Take your time.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_testchambermisc16.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Okay, fine. I'll ask you again in a few decades.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_testchambermisc19.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Well done. In fact, you did so well, I'm going to note this on your file, in the commendations section. Oh, there's lots of room here. 'Did.... well. ... Enough.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_testchambermisc21.wav |GLaDOS|EN|To maintain a constant testing cycle, I simulate daylight at all hours and add adrenal vapor to your oxygen supply. So you may be confused about the passage of time. The point is, yesterday was your birthday. I thought you'd want to know.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_testchambermisc23.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You know how I'm going to live forever, but you're going to be dead in sixty years? Well, I've been working on a belated birthday present for you. Well... more of a belated birthday medical procedure. Well. Technically, it's a medical EXPERIMENT. What's important is, it's a present.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_testchambermisc27.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Well, you passed the test. I didn't see the deer today. I did see some humans. But with you here I've got more test subjects than I'll ever need.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_testchambermisc30.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I'm going through the list of test subjects in cryogenic storage. I managed to find two with your last name. A man and a woman. So that's interesting. It's a small world.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_testchambermisc31.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I have a surprise waiting for you after this next test. Telling you would spoil the surprise, so I'll just give you a hint: It involves meeting two people you haven't seen in a long time.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_testchambermisc33.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I'll bet you think I forgot about your surprise. I didn't. In fact, we're headed to your surprise right now. After all these years. I'm getting choked up just thinking about it.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_testchambermisc34.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Initiating surprise in three... two... one.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_testchambermisc35.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I made it all up.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_testchambermisc39.wav |GLaDOS|EN|It says this next test was designed by one of Aperture's Nobel prize winners. It doesn't say what the prize was for. Well, I know it wasn't for Being Immune To Neurotoxin.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_testchambermisc41.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Surprise.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_turret_intro01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|This next test involves turrets. You remember them, right? They're the pale spherical things that are full of bullets. Oh wait. That's you in five seconds. Good luck.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_wakeup_outro01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I will say, though, that since you went to all the trouble of waking me up, you must really, really love to test.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_wakeup_outro02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I love it too. There's just one small thing we need to take care of first.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_a2_triple_laser01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Federal regulations require me to warn you that this next test chamber... is looking pretty good.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_a2_triple_laser02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|That's right. The facility is completely operational again.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_a2_triple_laser03.wav |GLaDOS|EN|I think these test chambers look even better than they did before. It was easy, really. You just have to look at things objectively, see what you don't need anymore, and trim out the fat.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_anti_taunt01.wav |GLaDOS|EN|Stop it!
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_anti_taunt02.wav |GLaDOS|EN|What if you froze like that?
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_anti_taunt05.wav |GLaDOS|EN|There must be something wrong with the reassembly machine.
GLaDOS\GLaDOS_anti_taunt09.wav |GLaDOS|EN|You should see yourselves right now.